# Tic-Tac-Toe

RESTful API for a simple tic-tac-toe game.

## API [/api/games]

### List All Games [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)


        

### Create a New Game [POST]


+ Request (application/json)
    
    + Body
    
            {
                "player1": "Test User",
                "player2": "Other User"
            }
    
        

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "id": 2,
                "player1": "Test User-x",
                "player2": "Other User-o",
                "board": [
                    null,
                    null,
                    null,
                    null,
                    null,
                    null,
                    null,
                    null,
                    null
                    ],
                "move": 0,
                "status": "In Progress"
            }    
            
